      • update

        public void update​(Account acc)
        This notifies our database of the changes made to an account It checks if the account that has been changed is premium then it iterates over the respective list. When it finds the index of the account's position in the list, it replaces the old version of the account with the new one.
        Parameters:
        acc - the changed version of the account.
